annotationA: Vacuolar H[+] ATPase M8.9 accessory subunit; Frizzled-2 binding; frizzled binding; receptor activity. annotationB: V-type proton ATPase subunit a; Essential component of the vacuolar proton pump (V- ATPase), a multimeric enzyme that catalyzes the translocation of protons across the membranes. Required for assembly and activity of the V-ATPase
